{"type": "article", "id": 28646, "title": "简洁的挂钟", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-24T06:50:27Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 67, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021714337XsCm35Y0KTrziSe.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>这款名为 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/38678055/LumeWheel-Minimalist-Clock\">LumeWheel</a> 的挂钟是印度设计师 Akshay Patil 的作品，参考了船的舵盘进行设计。Patil 省去了钟面，仅留下一个镂空的金属圆环，LED 灯的位置表示刻度，一大一小两个指针分别代表了分和秒，时针则由点亮的 LED 灯替代。LumeWheel 还会根据时间切换灯光颜色（午前蓝色，午后黄色），看上去科技感十足。挂钟目前还处于原型阶段，尚未投入生产。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171431RvefOj4DsL2YExCz.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171432bzivWjGcuE6s5qAl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171432IM5tNap398mAcZvf.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}